---
import DetailLayout from '../layouts/DetailLayout.astro';
---
<DetailLayout title="Wavve">

  <section class="site-section" id="section-project-info">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row mb-5 align-items-center">
        <div class="col-md-6 pr-lg-5 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
          <div id="wavveCarousel" class="carousel carousel-fade" data-ride="carousel" data-interval="3000">
            <div class="carousel-inner">
              <div class="carousel-item active">
                <div class="device-wrapper">
                  <div class="device" data-device="Pixel" data-orientation="portrait" data-color="black">
                    <div class="screen">
                      <img src="images/wavve_mobile_main.gif" class="img-fluid" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:fill;" />
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <div class="device-wrapper">
                  <div class="device" data-device="SurfacePro3" data-orientation="portrait" data-color="black">
                    <div class="screen">
                      <img src="images/wavve_tablet_main.gif" class="img-fluid" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:fill;" />
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <div class="device-wrapper">
                  <div class="device" data-device="SamsungTV" data-orientation="portrait" data-color="black">
                    <div class="screen">
                      <img src="images/wavve_tv_main.gif" class="img-fluid" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:fill;" />
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <div class="device-wrapper">
                  <div class="device" data-device="automotive" data-orientation="portrait" data-color="black">
                    <div class="screen">
                      <img src="images/wavve_ivi_main.gif" class="img-fluid" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:fill;" />
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="section-heading">
            <h2><strong>Wavve</strong></h2>
          </div>
          <p><span class="date"><span class="icon-calendar"></span> July 2022 - </span></p>
          <p class="lead">방송과 영화, 오리지널 콘텐츠를 제공하는 국내 대표 OTT 플랫폼</p>
          <p class="mb-5">유료 가입자 400만 이상 OTT 서비스의 Android Mobile · TV · IVI 전 플랫폼 개발
            <br>Clean Architecture · Jetpack Compose 기반 비즈니스 · UI 공용 모듈 개발로 약 90%의 전 플랫폼 코드 공용화 달성
            <br>GitLab CI/CD 파이프라인 구축 및 Android Profiler · MAT · Shark 기반 메모리 성능 개선 · ChromeCast 로직 개선
            <br>Datadog · Braze 기반 광고/마케팅 로직 개발 및 스플래시 · 아웃스트림 광고 신규 연동
          </p>
          <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=kr.co.captv.pooqV2">
            <img src="images/icons/google_play_badge.png" class="img-fluid google-play-badge">
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="site-section bg-light" id="section-works">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12 mb-5">
          <div class="section-heading text-center">
            <h2>My <strong>Works</strong></h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-12">
          <div class="resume-item mb-4" data-toggle="modal" href="#portfolioModal1">
            <h3>Android IVI 기반의 신규 애플리케이션 개발</h3>
            <span class="school">#jetpack_compose #clean_architecture #ivi #faurecia #benz #volvo #polestar</span>
          </div>
          <div class="resume-item mb-4" data-toggle="modal" href="#portfolioModal2">
            <h3>Multi-Platform 공용 모듈 개발 및 앱 개발 효율화</h3>
            <span class="school">#clean_architecture #jetpack_compose #version_catalog #webview #junit #mockk #turbine #espresso</span>
          </div>
          <div class="resume-item mb-4" data-toggle="modal" href="#portfolioModal3">
            <h3>화면/기능 개발</h3>
            <span class="school">#server_driven_ui #jetpack_compose #clean_architecture</span>
          </div>
          <div class="resume-item mb-4" data-toggle="modal" href="#portfolioModal4">
            <h3>앱 성능 개선</h3>
            <span class="school">#android_profiler #mat #shark #ci_cd #firebase #crashlytics #chromecast</span>
          </div>
          <div class="resume-item mb-4" data-toggle="modal" href="#portfolioModal5">
            <h3>광고/마케팅/데이터 관련 로직 개발</h3>
            <span class="school">#datadog #braze #ad_mediation #google_adid #event_logging</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Modal 1 -->
  <div class="portfolio-modal modal fade" id="portfolioModal1" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog"><div class="modal-content">
      <div class="close-modal" data-dismiss="modal"><div class="lr"><div class="rl"></div></div></div>
      <div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto"><div class="modal-body">
        <h3>Android IVI 기반의 신규 애플리케이션 개발</h3><br>
        <div id="carouselForModal1" class="carousel carousel-fade" data-ride="carousel">
          <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active"><img class="modal-img" src="images/screenshots/wavve/ivi_main/1.png"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="modal-img" src="images/screenshots/wavve/ivi_main/2.png"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="modal-img" src="images/screenshots/wavve/ivi_main/3.png"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="modal-img" src="images/screenshots/wavve/ivi_main/4.png"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="modal-img" src="images/screenshots/wavve/ivi_main/5.png"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="modal-img" src="images/screenshots/wavve/ivi_main/6.png"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="modal-img" src="images/screenshots/wavve/ivi_main/7.png"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="modal-img" src="images/screenshots/wavve/ivi_main/8.png"></div>
          </div>
          <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselForModal1" role="button" data-slide="prev"><div class="carousel-buttons"><i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i></div></a>
          <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselForModal1" role="button" data-slide="next"><div class="carousel-buttons"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></div></a>
        </div><br>
        <div class="detail-desc">
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbsp 네비게이션 구성 · 홈 화면 · 검색 화면 개발 및 Compose 기반 공용 UI 컴포넌트 · 비즈니스 로직 모듈 개발로 목표 대비 약 1개월 개발 기간 단축</h4></div>
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbsp Volvo · Polestar 테스트 기기 기반 실차 환경 검증 및 Benz · Volvo · Polestar 등 주요 자동차 회사와의 협업을 통한 품질 검증 및 이슈 대응</h4></div>
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbsp Faurecia Aptoide 앱스토어 배포 프로세스 관리 및 Benz Light-Test 통과</h4></div>
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbsp Firebase Crashlytics 기반 크래시 모니터링 적용</h4></div>
        </div>
      </div></div></div></div>
    </div></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Modal 2 -->
  <div class="portfolio-modal modal fade" id="portfolioModal2" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog"><div class="modal-content">
      <div class="close-modal" data-dismiss="modal"><div class="lr"><div class="rl"></div></div></div>
      <div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto"><div class="modal-body">
        <h3>Multi-Platform 공용 모듈 개발 및 앱 개발 효율화</h3><br>
        <div id="carouselForModal2" class="carousel carousel-fade" data-ride="carousel">
          <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active"><img class="modal-img" src="images/screenshots/wavve/multiplatform_main/mobile.png"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="modal-img" src="images/screenshots/wavve/multiplatform_main/tablet.png"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="modal-img" src="images/screenshots/wavve/multiplatform_main/tv.png"></div>
            <div class="carousel-item"><img class="modal-img" src="images/screenshots/wavve/multiplatform_main/automotive.png"></div>
          </div>
          <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselForModal2" role="button" data-slide="prev"><div class="carousel-buttons"><i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i></div></a>
          <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselForModal2" role="button" data-slide="next"><div class="carousel-buttons"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></div></a>
        </div><br>
        <div class="detail-desc">
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbsp Clean Architecture 기반 비즈니스 모듈 · Compose UI 컴포넌트 모듈 개발 및 Mobile · TV · IVI 전 플랫폼 적용, 플랫폼별 파편화된 로직 · 리소스 정리 및 toml 기반 라이브러리 버전 표준화</h4></div>
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbsp 화면 단위로 파편화된 웹뷰 처리 로직 통합, JavascriptInterface · 딥링크 동작 재정의 및 모듈 간 의존성 제거를 통한 재사용 가능한 웹뷰 프레임워크 개발</h4></div>
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbsp Mobile · TV · IVI 전 플랫폼 비즈니스 · UI 로직 약 90% 공용화 달성 및 개발 · 유지보수 시간 약 70% 감소</h4></div>
          <div class="detail-desc-items"><h4>✓&nbsp jUnit · MockK · Turbine · Espresso 기반 비즈니스 로직 · Flow · UI 테스트 수행을 통한 성능 개선 및 품질 관리</h4></div>
        </div>
      </div></div></div></div>
    </div></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Modal 3 -->
  <div class="portfolio-modal modal fade" id="portfolioModal3" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog"><div class="modal-content">
      <div class="close-modal" data-dismiss="modal"><div class="lr"><div class="rl"></div></div></div>
      <div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto"><div class="modal-body">
        <h3>화면/기능 개발</h3><br>
        <div id="carouselForModal3" class="carousel carousel-fade" data-ride="carousel">
          <div class="carousel-inner" style="height:360px;">
            <div class="carousel-item active" style="height:360px;"><img src="images/wavve_mobile_3.png" class="modal-img" style="object-fit:contain;height:360px;" /></div>
